      "content": "The candles have all burned down to mere stubs of wax, and the silence of this manor is heavier than the stone walls themselves. He is gone... and with him, the very light of my soul has been extinguished. I look into the darkness of the garden and I no longer see shadows; I see a welcome embrace. Why must I continue to endure this hollow ache when the night offers such a quiet, velvet peace?",
